SubjectCanada-Namibia- Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital ** Convention **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take, on behalf of Canada, the measures necessary to BRING INTO FORCE the CONVENTION between the Canada and the REPUBLIC OF NAMIBIA for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital.
